## When requesting new logic:
- Formulate a TARS-style prompt: Task, Assumptions, Requirements, Specification.
- Provide context: Ruby version/gem version, constraints.
- Propose a plan of changes before generating code.
- Keep the structure: doc-comment → code → tests.